            "title": "越秀地產4月份合同銷售按年增23.8% 首4個月累計升37%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">越秀地產(00123)公布，今年4月份實現合同銷售102.93億元(人民幣．下同)，按夫升23.8%；涉及樓面22.93萬平方米。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">若將今年首4個月合計，該公司累計合同銷售達411.2億元，較去年同期提升37%；涉及樓面92.45萬平方米，按年減少9.6%。累計合同銷售約佔全年銷售目標1205億元的34.1%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14913295-%e8%b6%8a%e7%a7%80%e5%9c%b0%e7%94%a24%e6%9c%88%e4%bb%bd%e5%90%88%e5%90%8c%e9%8a%b7%e5%94%ae%e6%8c%89%e5%b9%b4%e5%a2%9e23-8-%e9%a6%964%e5%80%8b%e6%9c%88%e7%b4%af%e8%a8%88%e5%8d%8737",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/11/00123.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-05-08 17:05:39",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "華虹首季溢利按年大跌逾88%   預期次季毛利率按季跌",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">華虹半導體(01347)首季母公司擁有人應佔溢利380萬(美元‧下同)，較去年同期3180萬元大減88.05%。上季度應佔虧損為2520萬元。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：華虹半導體官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/01/20250108_FI_source-web_01347.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：華虹半導體官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/01/20250108_FI_source-web_01347.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：華虹半導體官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">銷售收入5.41億元，按年升17.6%，按季升0.3%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">毛利率9.2%，按年升2.8百分點，按季跌2.2百分點。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">公司發出第二季指引預計次季銷售收入5.5億元至5.7億元，毛利率7%至9%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">總裁兼執行董白鵬表示，首季銷售收入及毛利率均符合指引，產能進度符合預期，但近期國際環境及政策變化，在客戶需求，採購成本及產業鏈格局均面臨較大不確定性。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14913275-%e8%8f%af%e8%99%b9%e9%a6%96%e5%ad%a3%e6%ba%a2%e5%88%a9%e6%8c%89%e5%b9%b4%e5%a4%a7%e8%b7%8c%e9%80%be88-%e9%a0%90%e6%9c%9f%e6%ac%a1%e5%ad%a3%e6%af%9b%e5%88%a9%e7%8e%87%e6%8c%89%e5%ad%a3%e8%b7%8c",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/05/20250507_FI_source-ap_01347.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-05-08 17:00:50",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "綠城中國上月自投項目銷售按年降20% 整體首4個月累計銷售減5.96%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">綠城中國(03900)公布，今年4月份自投項目銷售額約116億元(人民幣．下同)，按年減少20%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：綠城中國官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2023/08/20230825_FI_source-web_綠城中國.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：綠城中國官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2023/08/20230825_FI_source-web_綠城中國.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：綠城中國官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">自投項目於今年首4個月合同銷售477億元，歸屬於綠城的權益金額約298億元，分別較去年同期跌9.14%及19.68%。截至4月底，另有累計已簽認購協議但未轉銷售合同的金額約28億元，其中歸屬集團的權益金額約16億元。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">至於綠城代建項目於今年4月份銷售額約72億元；今年首4個月累計則達233億元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">綜合上述數字，綠城今年首4個月累計取得總合同銷售710億元，按年減少5.96%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14913205-%e7%b6%a0%e5%9f%8e%e4%b8%ad%e5%9c%8b%e4%b8%8a%e6%9c%88%e8%87%aa%e6%8a%95%e9%a0%85%e7%9b%ae%e9%8a%b7%e5%94%ae%e6%8c%89%e5%b9%b4%e9%99%8d20-%e6%95%b4%e9%ab%94%e9%a6%964%e5%80%8b%e6%9c%88%e7%b4%af",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/06/20230825_FI_source-web_03900_GREENTOWN_FB.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-05-08 16:55:43",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "碧桂園4月份合同銷售按年降20%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">碧桂園(02007)公布，今年4月份實現歸屬公司股東權益的合同銷售約30.8億元人民幣，按年降20%；涉及樓面約38萬平方米。</p>\n</div>",
